<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text"><i>Achnatherum hymenoides </i>tolerates fire because its open stands burn with little damage to the basal buds. Seedlings establish after fire from off-site seed sources. Plants may dominate the site within 4 years (Tirmenstein 1999a).</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
		<tr>
			<td class="key">Fire return interval</td>
			<td>Medium (7-70 years)
				
			</td>
		</tr>
		
